At 07:26 PM 1/26/05, Christophe Guilbert wrote:
>I am still try to see if I should rebuild my engine,
>I have 50, 75, 50, 75 PSI on a aircool 2000cc 1983 vanagon,
>We could not start the engine so the compression have been done with a cold engine,
